rComments: Tests aren't that hard but lectures make no sense and didn't get marks back to us in a timely manner.

Professor Bonner is a great prof! He mumbles a bit sometimes but otherwise very clear. Approachable, kind, and has fair assignments. Read everything and pay attention in class to get the grasp of the subject matter. Classes, assignments are easy-going. Midterms and exams need preparation beforehand. He will test whether you know the stuff or not.
